"I am home and I had almost forgotten its beauty."
– Spock, 2237 ("Yesteryear")
Ni'Var, formerly Vulcan, was an inhabited M-class planet in the Vulcan system of the Alpha Quadrant. It had no moons, but appeared to have close planetary companions.
